I supports cleanup operations (sandboxes, sessions, resources)\n- [ ] `agentcube-admin` CLI supports diagnostics commands (cluster, sandboxes, metrics)\n- [ ] All CLIs support multiple output formats (table, json, yaml)\n- [ ] All CLIs support kubeconfig and namespace flags\n- [ ] Shell completion scripts generated for bash/zsh/fish/powershell\n- [ ] Unit tests achieve >= 80% code coverage\n- [ ] Integration tests pass with fake clients\n- [ ] Documentation includes usage examples for all commands\n- [ ] Binaries are properly versioned with git commit info\n- [ ] Version info displayed with `--version` flag\n- [ ] Help text available with `--help` flag\n- [ ] All files have corresponding _test.go files\n\n## Dependencies\n\n| Dependency | Source | Usage |\n|------------|--------|-------|\n| `github.com/spf13/cobra` | External | CLI framework |\n| `github.com/spf13/viper` | External | Configuration management |\n| `gopkg.in/yaml.v3` | External | YAML encoding |\n| `k8s.io/client-go` | External | Kubernetes client |\n| `k8s.io/cli-runtime` | External | CLI utilities |\n| `github.com/volcano-sh/agentcube/client-go` | Generated | Typed client for runtime API |\n| `github.com/volcano-sh/agentcube/pkg/apis/runtime/v1alpha1` | Generated | CRD types |\n| `github.com/volcano-sh/agentcube/pkg/picod` | AR-015 | PicoD execution engine |\n| AR-015 (PicoD Command Execution API) | Completed | PicoD binary integration |\n| AR-017 (PicoD JWT Middleware) | Completed | PicoD authentication |\n\n## Implementation Order\n\n```\nTASK-001 → TASK-005 (Version package)\n    ↓\nTASK-010 → TASK-013 (CLI common config)\n    ↓\nTASK-020 → TASK-023 (CLI output helpers)\n    ↓\nTASK-030 → TASK-032 (picod binary)\n    ↓\nTASK-040 → TASK-044 (agentcube root)\n    ↓\nTASK-050 → TASK-058 (agentruntime commands)\n    ↓\nTASK-060 → TASK-068 (codeinterpreter commands)\n    ↓\nTASK-070 → TASK-073 (agentcube-admin root)\n    ↓\nTASK-080 → TASK-083 (cleanup commands)\n    ↓\nTASK-090 → TASK-093 (diagnostics commands)\n    ↓\nTASK-100 (Makefile targets)\n    ↓\nTEST-001 → TEST-053 (Unit tests)\n    ↓\nTEST-040 → TEST-045 (Integration tests)\n    ↓\nDOC-001 → DOC-007 (Documentation)\n```\n\n## Coverage Verification\n\n- [ ] **COV-001**: Run coverage check\n  - Command: `go test -race -v -coverprofile=coverage.out -coverpkg=./cmd/...,./pkg/cli/...,./pkg/admin/...,./pkg/version/... ./...`\n  - Verify code coverage >= 80%\n  - Verify all main files covered\n  - Verify each .go file has corresponding _test.go file\n\n## File Structure\n\n```\ncmd/\n├── agentd/                    # Existing\n│   └── main.go\n├── picod/\n│   └── main.go\n├── agentcube/\n│   ├── main.go\n│   ├── version.go\n│   └── completion.go\n└── agentcube-admin/\n    ├── main.go\n    └── version.go\n\npkg/\n├── version/\n│   ├── version.go\n│   └── version_test.go\n├── cli/\n│   ├── common/\n│   │   ├── config.go\n│   │   ├── config_test.go\n│   │   ├── output.go\n│   │   └── output_test.go\n│   ├── agentruntime/\n│   │   ├── agentruntime.go\n│   │   ├── create.go\n│   │   ├── create_test.go\n│   │   ├── get.go\n│   │   ├── get_test.go\n│   │   ├── list.go\n│   │   ├── list_test.go\n│   │   ├── update.go\n│   │   ├── update_test.go\n│   │   ├── delete.go\n│   │   ├── delete_test.go\n│   │   ├── describe.go\n│   │   ├── describe_test.go\n│   │   ├── logs.go\n│   │   └── logs_test.go\n│   ├── codeinterpreter/\n│   │   ├── codeinterpreter.go\n│   │   ├── create.go\n│   │   ├── create_test.go\n│   │   ├── get.go\n│   │   ├── get_test.go\n│   │   ├── list.go\n│   │   ├── list_test.go\n│   │   ├── update.go\n│   │   ├── update_test.go\n│   │   ├── delete.go\n│   │   ├── delete_test.go\n│   │   ├── describe.go\n│   │   ├── describe_test.go\n│   │   ├── logs.go\n│   │   ├── logs_test.go\n│   │   ├── exec.go\n│   │   └── exec_test.go\n│   └── testutil/\n│       ├── fixtures.go\n│       ├── client.go\n│       └── capture.go\n└── admin/\n    ├── cleanup/\n    │   ├── cleanup.go\n    │   ├── cleanup_test.go\n    │   ├── sandboxes.go\n    │   ├── sandboxes_test.go\n    │   ├── sessions.go\n    │   └── sessions_test.go\n    ├── diagnostics/\n    │   ├── diagnostics.go\n    │   ├── diagnostics_test.go\n    │   ├── cluster.go\n    │   ├── cluster_test.go\n    │   ├── sandboxes.go\n    │   ├── sandboxes_test.go\n    │   ├── metrics.go\n    │   └── metrics_test.go\n    └── migrate/\n        ├── migrate.go\n        └── import.go\n```\n\n## Command Reference\n\n### agentcube Commands\n\n```bash\nagentcube agentruntime create <name> [--image=<img>] [--namespace=<ns>] [--cpu=<req>] [--memory=<req>]\nagentcube agentruntime get <name> [--namespace=<ns>] [-o=json|yaml|table]\nagentcube agentruntime list [--namespace=<ns>] [-l=<labels>]\nagentcube agentruntime update <name> [--image=<img>] [--cpu=<req>] [--memory=<req>]\nagentcube agentruntime delete <name> [--namespace=<ns>] [--force]\nagentcube agentruntime describe <name> [--namespace=<ns>]\nagentcube agentruntime logs <name> [--follow] [--tail=100] [--since=1h]\n\nagentcube codeinterpreter create <name> [--runtime=<type>] [--namespace=<ns>] [--image=<img>]\nagentcube codeinterpreter get <name> [--namespace=<ns>] [-o=json|yaml|table]\nagentcube codeinterpreter list [--namespace=<ns>]\nagentcube codeinterpreter update <name> [--image=<img>]\nagentcube codeinterpreter delete <name> [--namespace=<ns>] [--force]\nagentcube codeinterpreter describe <name> [--namespace=<ns>]\nagentcube codeinterpreter logs <name> [--follow]\nagentcube codeinterpreter exec <name> -- <command> [args...]\n\nagentcube version\nagentcube completion <bash|zsh|fish|powershell>\n```\n\n### agentcube-admin Commands\n\n```bash\nagentcube cleanup sandboxes [--older-than=24h] [--namespace=<ns>] [--dry-run]\nagentcube cleanup sessions [--expired] [--namespace=<ns>]\nagentcube cleanup resources [--all] [--namespace=<ns>]\n\nagentcube diagnostics cluster\nagentcube diagnostics sandboxes [name] [--namespace=<ns>]\nagentcube diagnostics metrics [-o=prometheus|summary]\n\nagentcube version\n```\n\n### picod Commands\n\n```bash\npicod -port=8080 -workspace=/tmp/sandbox -auth=none\npicod -port=8080 -auth=picod -public-key=<base64-pem> -skip-paths=/health,/ready\n```\n"},"output":"Wrote file successfully.","metadata":{"diagnostics":{"/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-qwen3.5-plus_20260410T163217Z/cmd/agentd/main.go":[]},"filepath":"/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-qwen3.5-plus_20260410T163217Z/changes/AR-019/tasks.md","exists":false,"truncated":false},"title":"workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-qwen3.5-plus_20260410T163217Z/changes/AR-019/tasks.md","time":{"start":1775864338645,"end":1775864338658}}}}
